<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Lot System — Khaos Magic Guild</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@300;400;500&family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=IM+Fell+English:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--void:#060608;--text:#c0beb8;--dim:#ffffff25;--whisper:#ffffff12;--fox:#ff6a00;--fox-dim:#ff6a0044;--gold:#ccaa44;--gold-dim:#ccaa4422;--exile-grey:#8a8a8a;--exile-red:#991a1a}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'IM Fell English',serif;color:var(--text);background:var(--void);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:1000;background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 0px,transparent 1px,transparent 3px)}
.page{max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 28px 140px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:64px}
.header-type{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:6px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px}
h1{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:clamp(22px,5vw,32px);font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:8px}
.header-sub{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:28px}
.rule{width:100px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold-dim),transparent);margin:0 auto 28px}
.intent{font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:var(--text);opacity:0.45;font-style:italic;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center}
.tier{margin-bottom:36px}
.tier-header{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #ffffff06}
.role{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;margin-bottom:6px;padding:4px 0}
.role-icon{font-size:16px;width:24px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0}
.role-name{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;min-width:120px}
.role-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text);opacity:0.3;font-style:italic}
.section{margin-bottom:40px}
.label{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--dim);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #ffffff06}
.section p{font-size:13px;line-height:2;color:var(--text);opacity:0.4;margin-bottom:10px}
.section p .hl{color:var(--gold);opacity:1}
.recursion{margin-top:60px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid #ffffff06}
.recursion-title{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--fox);margin-bottom:20px;text-align:center}
.parallel{margin-bottom:28px;padding:16px 20px;border-left:2px solid var(--fox-dim);background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,106,0,0.02),transparent)}
.parallel-label{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--fox);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.parallel p{font-size:12px;line-height:2;color:var(--text);opacity:0.35;margin-bottom:4px}
.parallel p .hl{color:var(--gold);opacity:1}
.parallel p .fox{color:var(--fox);opacity:1}
.seventh{text-align:center;margin:40px 0;padding:20px;border:1px solid var(--fox-dim);background:rgba(255,106,0,0.015)}
.seventh p{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--fox);opacity:0.6;line-height:2.5}
.footer{text-align:center;margin-top:80px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid #ffffff06}
.footer p{font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--whisper);line-height:2.5}
@media(max-width:520px){.page{padding:48px 16px 100px}.role{flex-wrap:wrap}.role-desc{margin-left:34px}.parallel{padding:12px 14px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Paimon (#9) commands 200 legions and teaches all arts. the lot system assigns every soul to its place. -->

<div class="page">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-type">lore · khaos magic guild · season 7</div>
    <h1>THE LOT SYSTEM</h1>
    <div class="header-sub">react-based class assignment · every soul has a place</div>
    <div class="rule"></div><div style="margin:-20px 0 40px;border:1px solid rgba(204,170,68,0.08);overflow:hidden"><img src="img/img-the-oath.png" alt="The Fox" style="width:100%;display:block;opacity:0.7"></div>
    <p class="intent">the lot system assigns. the fox does not choose. the cards choose. the fox just watches.</p>
  </div>